<header class="bg-zinc-900 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center p-10 md:p-20 gap-6 text-center md:text-left rounded-xl shadow-lg">
    <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold pb-4 text-white">Protect Your Password</h1>
        <p class="my-4 text-lg text-gray-300">
            Your password is the key to your digital world. Using weak or repeated passwords can put your personal and financial data at risk.  
            <span class="font-semibold text-indigo-400">Enable multi-factor authentication, use a password manager, and create strong, unique passwords.</span>
        </p>

        <ul class="text-gray-400 text-sm space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>✅ Use at least 12 characters</li>
            <li>✅ Include uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and symbols</li>
            <li>✅ Avoid common words and personal information</li>
            <li>✅ Change your passwords regularly</li>
        </ul>

        <button class="bg-indigo-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-lg font-medium shadow-md hover:bg-indigo-400 transition-all">
            Start Now
        </button>
    </div>

    <img src="images/fingerprint.svg" class="w-64 md:w-80 drop-shadow-lg" alt="Fingerprint security">
</header>
